{
  "texts": [
    "Both machine learning and deep learning techniques are harnessed to automate the accurate categorization of images, enabling efficient and effective decision-making.",
    "The Sect. 1 elaborates the insights of the image processing operations.",
    "In Sect. 2 of this paper, a comprehensive overview of the evaluation metrics employed for various image processing operations is provided.",
    "Moving to Sect. 3, an in-depth exploration unfolds concerning the diverse range of Deep Learning (DL) models specifically tailored for image preprocessing tasks.",
    "Within Sect. 4, a thorough examination ensues, outlining the array of DL methods harnessed for image segmentation tasks, unraveling their techniques and applications."
  ]
}